lead_paragraph: Sheldon McClellan scored 22 points, Ja'Quan Newton made two big 3-pointers in the second half and No. 13 Miami relied on defense to get past Syracuse 64-51 on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: No. 13 Miami Pulls Away Late to Beat Syracuse 64-51
